00:26:02,672 --> 00:26:04,079
<i>Aqui!</i>

317
00:26:06,221 --> 00:26:07,528
<i>Vamos!</i>

318
00:26:07,530 --> 00:26:09,262
Venha!

319
00:26:09,588 --> 00:26:10,966
Não.

320
00:26:13,506 --> 00:26:16,216
Atire na cabeça, por favor.

321
00:26:16,272 --> 00:26:17,681
Boa caçada.

322
00:26:39,336 --> 00:26:40,849
O que aconteceu?

323
