473
00:43:14,920 --> 00:43:16,369
Chave.

474
00:43:16,905 --> 00:43:18,302
Precisamos ir.

475
00:43:25,554 --> 00:43:28,114
Travis!
Precisamos ir, agora!

476
00:43:28,116 --> 00:43:29,962
Charlene! Vai, vai!

477
00:43:31,015 --> 00:43:32,450
Nick, atrás de você.

478
00:43:35,735 --> 00:43:37,478
<i>Atirem!</i>

479
00:43:50,264 --> 00:43:51,613
Mãe!

480
00:43:56,846 --> 00:43:59,579
